title: Am i the only one who didnt expect C9 to show up so good?
body: This team has shown such godlike playing so far... But i guess anything is possible in a time where you see a mordekaiser ADC at worlds.

replies.body:
Montecristo didn't.

But honestly, no one EXPECTED it.
